    <svcproc svcproctype="PROCTYPE" graphiccount="0">
        <title>ELECTRONIC CONTROL MODULE (ECM)</title>
        <para>The ECM prevents the engine from being cranked if the engine is already running. It does this by not
            allowing the Engine Crank Inhibit relay from being enabled.
        </para>
